h1 User Verification
hr
div(ng-controller = "VerifyController as verify")
	p(ng-if = "!verify.loaded")
		| Verifying...
	p(ng-if = "verify.loaded")
		.text-success(ng-if = "verify.verified") Been verified! Feel free to log in 
			| and enjoy the full functionality of the site.
		.text-danger(ng-if = "!verify.verified") Verification failed!  Verification 
			| tokens only last for one hour after the email is sent. Perhaps you waited 
			| too long?
			br
			br
			| If that's not the case, and you still can't verify your email with the site, 
			| please contact Seth.
	p(ng-if = "verify.loaded && !verify.verified")
		a.col-xs-6(class = "btn btn-danger" ng-click = "profile.resendVerificationEmail()") Resend Verification
